message: The activity identifier must be different to the organisation identifier of the reporting organisation.

The activity identifier should begin with your IATI organisation identifier (either the current IATI Organisation identifier for the reporting organisation or a previous version included in other-identifier element) followed by a unique string for the activity separated by a hyphen
The reporting organisation id must start with an approved agency code.
The activity must have a planned start date or an actual start date.
Each activity must have a specified sector, either at activity level OR for all transactions.
